       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CKYQUEUE2.
      * CKYCR UPDATE QUEUE ROUTING FOR THE SEVEN-DAY SUBMISSION SLA.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-QUEUE-AGE PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-ROUTE     PIC X(8) VALUE 'PENDING'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-QUEUE-AGE
           PERFORM 2000-CHOOSE-ROUTE
           DISPLAY 'ROUTE: ' WS-ROUTE
           STOP RUN.
       2000-CHOOSE-ROUTE.
           MOVE 'PENDING' TO WS-ROUTE
           IF WS-QUEUE-AGE > 7
              MOVE 'EXPEDITE' TO WS-ROUTE
           ELSE
              MOVE 'STANDARD' TO WS-ROUTE
           END-IF.
